Functional Requirements:
- The system should allow students to register and create a new account
- The system should allow students to log in using their credentials
- The system should allow students to view the dashboard (home page) upon successful login
- The system should allow students to view a list of courses that are available
- The system should allow students to view course details
- The system should allow students to enroll in a course
- The system should allow students to view their enrolled courses in the dashboard
- The system should allow students to complete quizzes
- The system should allow students to view their quiz results and total score
- The system should track the status of courses enrolled by the student
- The system should generate a certificate upon completion of courses
- The system should allow students to view their certificates
- The system should allow students to download their certificates
- The system should allow admins to add new courses
- The system should allow admins to delete existing courses
- The system should allow admins to create quizzes

Non-functional requirements:
- The system should be user-friendly for students
- The system should allow users to navigate between pages easily
- The system should allow multiple students to access the program simultaneously
- The system should respond within seconds
- The system should only allow admin privileges to admins only
- The system should protect student's login credentials
